snippet: So Yeon Ryu rode a string of six birdies in the middle of her round to a nine-under-par 62 and a seven-stroke victory in the L.P.G.A’s Jamie Farr Toledo Classic in Sylvania, Ohio.
abstract: So Yeon Ryu wins the LPGA’s Jamie Farr Toledo Classic golf tournament.
lead_paragraph: So Yeon Ryu rode a string of six birdies in the middle of her round to a nine-under-par 62 and a seven-stroke victory in the L.P.G.A’s Jamie Farr Toledo Classic in Sylvania, Ohio.
